	---------------------
	|Business components| 
	---------------------
	 
	- User: CRUD, account/profile: information fields, change user infos
	- Registration: create user registration, send confirmation link, activate user account 
	- Messaging: send messages, persist messages, 
	- Dashboard: Chats , Contacts, Settings
	- Performance monitoring: exposing runtime data such as number of exceptions, method execution time via JMX : MXBeans